  • How do I cancel my ticket?
    Please go to customer support section of makemytrip.com (Top right corner on website) and proceed to cancel your ticket. You will be asked to enter booking Id and Contact number.     0 to 1 day before travel - 100 % of the total fare
    1 day to 2 days before travel - 50 % of the total fare
    2 days before travel - 20 % of the total fare
